original: Lundgren, Rolf, länsbokhållare, Jönköping, f. 27/1/09 i Uppsala av Per Rickard L. o. Elisabet Eriksson. G. 41 m. Kristina Hultman. Barn: Anders f. 42. — Stud:ex. v. Upp^s. h. a. 1. 28, jur. kand. v. Upps. univ. 3(). Doms :tjg. v. Bollnäs doms. 36-39, anst. s. länsbokhåll. v. länsstyr. i Västerås 39-44, v. länsstyr. i Jönköp. fr. 45.
translated: Lundgren, Rolf, county bookkeeper, Jönköping, b. 27/1/09 in Uppsala to Per Rickard L. and Elisabet Eriksson. Married in 1941 to Kristina Hultman. Children: Anders, b. 1942. Completed secondary school at Uppsala high school, natural science field, in 1928. Obtained a law degree from Uppsala University in 1930. Worked as a court clerk at Bollnäs court from 1936-1939, employed as a county bookkeeper at the county administration in Västerås from 1939-1944, and at the county administration in Jönköping from 1945 onwards.
